22:41.327 --> 22:43.461
SuperVote.
The power is in your hands.

22:43.463 --> 22:46.297
<i>They'll sing for your votes.
Instagram, Facebook and Twitter.</i>

22:46.299 --> 22:48.499
- Phillip Phillips!
<i>- (Crowd cheers)</i>

